{"tid":1881250,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"老有所依！ 美股10年大牛市造就眾多百萬富翁","createTime":"2020-02-15T12:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T02:00:38.000Z","uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1ed56e52590aa3e9a2c519c106c772c7d2e7f5a7","tid":1881250,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T12:03:48.000Z","msg":"根據富達投資（Fidelity Investments）的最新數據，該公司旗下401k和IRA等退休儲蓄賬戶中的百萬富翁數量達到了創紀錄的新高，而這在很大程度上必須要歸因於美股市場的大漲。過去十年時間裡，標普500指數累計漲幅達到188.88%，而單單去年第四季度的漲幅就達到了8.53%。<br />\n<br />\n具體而言，401k賬戶中，<span style=\"color: red;\">淨資產值至少達到100萬美元的，總數量第四季度達到了23.3萬個，超過第三季度的20萬個，也比十年前美股牛市剛剛開始走出金融危機時多了21.2萬個</span>。<br />\n<br />\nIRA方面也可以看到類似的軌跡。截至2019年年底，IRA百萬富翁的數量環比增長14%，達到了20.8萬個​​，一舉刷新了第三季度創下的18.24萬的歷史紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n富達的這些數據是來自於他們託管下的1730萬401k和990萬IRA退休儲蓄賬戶。<br />\n<img src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JgdM3yePzR86KD28mFawEPXWkpqNhg3aLickcXibykevKGpPFzQjqEZKHicVdUWyZd0vFY1ibXhGgP3gVaj0qPb7kg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FJgdM3yePzR86KD28mFawEPXWkpqNhg3aLickcXibykevKGpPFzQjqEZKHicVdUWyZd0vFY1ibXhGgP3gVaj0qPb7kg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26wx_co%3D1&h=cfe0cee2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n富達的數據顯示，401k賬戶的平均資產規模為11.23萬美元，同比增長17%。<br />\n<br />\n這些百萬富翁退休儲蓄者的進展，除了股市令人印象深刻的漲勢&mdash;&mdash;比如標普500指數第四季度的漲幅高達8.53%&mdash;&mdash;之外，也要歸功於他們堅持不懈的長期投資。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;從這些401k百萬富翁身上，<span style=\"color: red;\">我們看到，他們都是在長達三十年的生涯當中一直堅持儲蓄</span>。&rdquo;富達副總裁墨菲（Meghan Murphy）表示，&ldquo;其中一些人會將<span style=\"color: red;\">每年收入的25%都投入儲蓄</span>。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n不過，2019年年底的美股大漲，受益者當然不僅僅只有這些百萬富翁儲蓄者。<br />\n<img src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JgdM3yePzR86KD28mFawEPXWkpqNhg3arKfVUFe4PlbF0vvVIyQPjNvILCGC9d74qMLZTRlGtrToYOU06XEuQQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FJgdM3yePzR86KD28mFawEPXWkpqNhg3arKfVUFe4PlbF0vvVIyQPjNvILCGC9d74qMLZTRlGtrToYOU06XEuQQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26wx_co%3D1&h=90892946&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n那些儲蓄週期達到十年的人們，他們的平均賬戶資產在第四季度結束時增至32.82萬美元，較之一個季度之前增加了2.1萬美元以上。<br />\n<br />\n整體而言，全部401k賬戶資產平均增至11.23萬美元，同比增幅17%，全體IRA賬戶資產平均增至11.54萬美元，同比增幅也是17%。<br />\n<br />\n宏觀角度看，<span style=\"color: red;\">33%的投資者在2019年都提升了其儲蓄率。具體來說，40%的人是自己主動提升了供款額度</span>，而其他人則是自動提升額度的機制使然。<br />\n<br />\n過去十年當中，標普500指數累計漲幅達到188.88%，而那些這十年來一直在儲蓄的千禧世代，他們的資產規模也達到了新高，第四季度結束時平均為14.98萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6516678cd2b333cf8a747cb8a562eb8b43ab6b","tid":1881250,"uid":152630,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T12:09:47.000Z","msg":"如果係中國30年堅持儲蓄應該破左產"},{"pid":"7d7b2f1b50822b80c2b24d3453b8f19895c7c2ea","tid":1881250,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T12:58:21.000Z","msg":"on9廣告文....<br />\n連投資性具風險產品同存蓄都唔分想引9人買/加額 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177a7036d42f5d4d806a84cbc583bdd9ca717c06","tid":1881250,"uid":259777,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T13:15:33.000Z","msg":"其實唔單只美股做到<br />\n港股只要你30年嚟不斷分散投資<br />\n每月供盈富/唔同股票<br />\n其實回報係跑贏樓市"},{"pid":"a6bd0d5e0f100a86171b7389422af9b4a5f414fa","tid":1881250,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T17:48:00.000Z","msg":"唉  羨慕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8720a2d1378b452d99058459c4f77afb35de89de","tid":1881250,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:39:44.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"505ff88e73f64917d00e3534ac91347965bbf350","tid":1881250,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8720a2d1378b452d99058459c4f77afb35de89de","tid":1881250,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:39:44.000Z","msg":"lm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:48:33.000Z","msg":"百萬富翁係香港有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc758ad18b01ad19ef3a254783d31fd8f5c5d21","tid":1881250,"uid":28131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:00:38.000Z","msg":"係連登post 呢d有撚用咩 連登仔賭錢玩牛熊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}